textBeforeTable: 2015 Tour Dates Katie Melua Tickets - Her Unique SoundAnd why was she so redefining? It was simple. Try to take a tasteful mix of jazzy vocals enhanced with a bit of pop style and -- brace yourself on this one -- some adult contemporary sway! That's Katie Melua for you. Moreover, her second album featured some inventive worldbeat sounds and jazz-pop mixes -- as if she could never stun a crowd with her innovation again! Katie Melua Tickets - The Music of MeluaHer debut album was titled Call Off the Search, and that's certainly what the music industry did. They found a tremendous star not only with talent, but innovation. Some of her best included the single 'Closest Thing to Crazy' hitting number one in December of 2003, and by the next year it was inevitable that Call Off the Search would go platinum with 300,000 units sold in Great Britain alone. The album actually went platinum an astronomical six times! 2005 was the year of her second effort, entitled Piece by Piece, featuring even more of Melua's massive innovation in a music phenomenon that could only redefine the heavily stereotyped 'young starlet' stigma. Katie Melua Tickets - Not Just Another Pretty StarletThis was the rage of the U.K., really: a young Soviet Georgia singer born in 1984 by the name of Katie Melua.
